hesml.benchmarks.impl

Class BenchmarkCrossICModelMeasures

  • java.lang.Object
    • hesml.benchmarks.impl.AbstractBenchmark
      • hesml.benchmarks.impl.WordNetSimBenchmark
        • hesml.benchmarks.impl.BenchmarkCrossICModelMeasures
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISimilarityBenchmark

    class BenchmarkCrossICModelMeasures
extends WordNetSimBenchmark
    This class implements a set of cross-validation benchmarks by computing the correlation values for the experimental matrix defined by the Cartesian product of a set of intrinsic IC models versus a set of IC-based similarity measures. The benchmark computes the Pearson and Spearman correlation values for each pair (IC model, IC measure).
